%% Diagram: QPACK Required Insert Count blocks one stream, not all
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant E as Encoder
    participant ES as Encoder stream (uni 0x02)
    participant RS as Request stream
    participant D as Decoder
    participant DS as Decoder stream (uni 0x03)

    E->>ES: Insert "x-custom: value" → dynamic table index 62
    E->>RS: Header block, Required Insert Count = 63

    Note over D: Request stream arrives first
    Note over D: Required Insert Count (63) > current (62) → block this stream only

    ES->>D: Dynamic table update arrives
    Note over D: Insert count now 63 — unblock the request stream

    D->>DS: Section Acknowledgment (frees encoder buffer)
